Vile smirks as he watches Trainwreck sustain the firepower, however he would 
not be able to do that for much longer.

Vile: "Gemini, form the Gemini Dragon and teach this train to have respect 
for the past!"

Gemini 1 and 2 nod before each leaps up high into the air and glows. The 
clouds above begins to swirl. Thunder begins to crackle as the sounds of 
transforming can be heard from a above a second later the clouds literally 
are sent scattering as a massive "meched out" double headed dragon around 45 
feet tall descends from them, its massive wings flapping wildly as 18 square 
like objects surround it. Both heads roar loudly and then speak at the same 
time their voice having an echo to it.

Gemini Dragon: "Destruction shall be dealt unto all..."

Vile looks up at the massive beast and smirks before he flys back and away 
from Trainwreck a nice Distance. Methos who is ontop of Trainwreck also looks 
up at Gemini Dragon. He then somehow sweatdrops and then flys off Trainwreck 
as if he was being chased by an army of Maximals with spark extractors. Up in 
the air the Gemini Dragon's right head shoots forward and unleashes a massive 
stream of flame at Trainwreck, at the same time the left head shoots out a 
nice large stream of liquid Nitrogen at the wheels of the chosen mafia 
member... From the front Vile unleashes another two antimatter blasts at 
Trainwreck.

--part1_54.1753b409.2882417c_boundary
